{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给张鼎的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给张鼎的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年5月7日）张鼎先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年十月廿五日来信？，又毛泽覃等照片，收到。感谢你的好意。入党事要在当地经过一定规章办理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此复，顺颂康吉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年五月七日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]张鼎，早年曾在毛泽东、何叔衡等主办的自修大学附设补习学校学习。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[2]张鼎在给毛泽东的信中，寄来他的“履历关系片断”，请求办理入党手续，并寄来他早年同毛泽覃等共青团支部成员的合影照片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[3]毛泽覃，毛泽东之弟，1935年牺牲。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":7}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":339,"page_end":339},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}